    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely flawless and looks like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I've pampered this car since day one, and it's honestly in pristine, 'like-new' condition inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that feels and smells brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. It's been garage-kept and loved, and I'd love for it to go to a great new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
