      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional specimen of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit maintains factory compression across all cylinders, with the double-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal phase timing. The chassis is structurally immaculate; the rear subframe mounting points have been proactively reinforced to ensure peak torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing original components in flawless condition. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, free of any aerodynamic imperfections or paint degradation, while the interior preserves the tactile integrity of the Nappa leather and brushed aluminum trim. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
