    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in impeccable condition, having been preserved to showroom standards with meticulous attention to detail. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of uncompromising care. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class for the most discerning of clients.",
