    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve kept it garaged and pampered, so it\u2019s completely flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, come take a look! It drives like a dream and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have.",
      "price": 44500.0,
